Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a state permit if you want to do business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlicensed prostitutes cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make much money if I abide by the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need his permission, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce me to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come here as many times as I \N need to until you let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man they call the Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:31.13,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,105)\pos(347,310)}Be My Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use your hands to catch it, \N because you are not a goalkeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules don't apply to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to stay with you for a while because \N he found the man he was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks I'll look after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is out of touch for a while, and \N he goes and picks up a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happened to our plan of him becoming \N an underground doctor and making a fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should get serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice header!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do that for, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said you can't touch the ball with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a yellow card for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to live my life \N if I am scared of things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are gonna get a red card if you \N keep saying stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:37.69,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,134)\pos(348,283)}Frankfurt Central Station
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are late...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and give me the stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while, Detective Messner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you called me that back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was our first meeting, and you \N never asked me what my profession was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I am no longer a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, you are no longer a detective, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Officer discharged for possession of narcotics."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very surprised when I found \N this article from six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recommend getting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a gun pointed at you under my coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you about the event that took \N place in Heidelberg ten months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as who hired you for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took the lives of the Fortners \N and the reporter, Mauler!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only the lookout!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who did it was my partner, Müller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Müller quit right after that incident, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got a lot of money for that, and should \N be living the high life right about now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, you used up all your money on \N narcotics, and this is your current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the one who accepted the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the one who committed the murders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he is the one who received most of the reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone once tried to kill me \N to keep my mouth shut, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved by a certain syndicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain syndicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked too much the other day, also!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are suffering from withdrawal symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as long as I'm sitting here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't think the dealer will come near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved by the Baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baby...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the bar named Candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can meet him there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big time extreme rightist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has high positions in both parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baby went to the east side \N after the Wall fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and tried to build a town of pure Germans...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he failed, so he came back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did a man like that save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Berlin Wall fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a great darkness was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster... was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told the rest to that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came at me, pointing her gun, out for revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The daughter of the couple we killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Anna...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Nina Fortner come to see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The Baby told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she should ever show up, I had \N to point her in his direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...very important bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have guts, coming here every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I'll buy you at a good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one who said I would get hurt if  I did \N business without the Baby's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, you little...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she the one who wanted to see the Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait on top of that seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is "Be My Baby," by the Ronettes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baby said it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:10:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country would be okay if a second Hitler was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your other name is Anna Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But neither is your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Names have so very little meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is the Baby, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you know where my brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to do once you meet \N your brother, dressed, like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't wave a dangerous thing like that around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Johan will show up to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I used to live here when I was a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I know all the back roads in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a pawnshop up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to trade in this carpet for some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  You don't have money, Mr. Heckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to get some cash for your dinner here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thankful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This entire area has turned into a Turkish district!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This design!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This texture!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly hand-woven silk \N no matter how you look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is synthetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since I feel sorry for you, I'll take it for 100 marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this store was still owned by a German, \N he would have paid me at least 10,000 Marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come looking for me after you \N realize that it was actually real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you call the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Hereke 100% silk carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a closer look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the small, fine details are elegantly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is worth 150,000 Marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It has to be a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if your discerning eyes can't even tell that this is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was real...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing was the genuine article!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is worth 150,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know where to sell it, you could get 800,000 Marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lets go eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can make that thing ours, we will \N be able to eat all we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is with that glare?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is too loud, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think you are doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but if you are looking for a \N customer, look somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If an Asian guy like yourself walks \N in there, he might get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place is a den for the right wingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a Turkish woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you are okay doing business around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do business in a dump like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend was kidnapped by some people in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she found out their secret or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to save her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what they have done to her by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl that I know is in there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of girl is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be a girl with long, blond hair...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of hair style she has now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was just taken away in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since she was with the Baby, probably to his mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of car was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What color?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big, bright red Benz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to find that car and go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you save my friend, also?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a child waiting for her at home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll take your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now please, go right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the girl the Baby brought in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite a beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised that you are Johan's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am professor Göderich.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one in the picture with Johan is General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two others...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The syndicate is composed of us four.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about some fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he knows that you are here, he will definitely show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't know where Johan is either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are in need of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he can be at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how Hitler obtained so much power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was very smart, with a head for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he knew three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He controlled the banks, commanded the defense \N industry, and seized the military...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Johan is doing one of those three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think my deductions are correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do with Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it was his charisma that allowed \N him to achieve all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitler failed his art school entrance exam, and \N was stuck as a corporal in the military...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If was some time after the age of thirty \N when he finally became charismatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has had monstrous charisma since he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you must not forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the first ones to put faith in Christ were the \N three wise men from the east and John the Baptist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The existence of these four amazing people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We four have paid close attention to \N Johan's talents since he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until Johan shows up to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you won't try to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have already taken one step inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for Johan here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, have some fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you have finally come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no broken bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:19:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing the questioning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do after you find Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm doing the questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to ask any questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina is an important guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not trash like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she is very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she has a cute face, she is trying to kill Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like that must be disposed of eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Nina is just a tool to lure Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people trying to--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked another question!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You foreign races don't have the right to ask us questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of impertinent attitude is the \N reason the entire town will be burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The entire town...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow night, the sky will be dyed a beautiful color.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here, I'll meet Johan..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the third floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your German is kind of awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What country are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Turkish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... going to be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are being held by the people here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stay here no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't hurry, my child will die also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow night, we are throwing \N a welcoming party for Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superior races like our own should be \N the only ones to exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest should burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... heard them... talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are going... to burn the entire city... tomorrow night...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Turkish district... they are going to burn it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
